      <div class="accordion">

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <a>Who is DealerGuy?</a>
          <div class="content">
            <p>
              DealerGuy is a personal full stack responsive project, built by Noam Kanonich.<br>
              The project involve JavaScript, Node.js, Express, HTML, CSS, MongoDB, Rate Limiter and more.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <a>What does DealerGuy do?</a>
          <div class="content">
            <p>By searching a product, DealerGuy will give you the best top 10 products list from Amazon<br>
              and from eBay, with relevent information and data to help you make the right decisions <br>
              before buying the product.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <a>Does DealerGuy provide an API?</a>
